# Private notes (optional)

Copy to repo root as `DEPLOYMENT.private.md` (gitignored). Fill in **your** URLs and secrets there — do not commit that file.

## Vercel (minimum)

- `UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL`
- `UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN`
- `ADMIN_SECRET` — long random string, same value for owner edit APIs

Optional: `TELEGRAM_NOTIFY_BOT_TOKEN`, `TELEGRAM_NOTIFY_CHAT_ID`, `SITE_PUBLIC_URL`

Set for Production + Preview, then redeploy.

## Your copy can include (not in Git)

- Bookmarked admin / moderation URL on your domain
- How you import `ADMIN_SECRET` on phone or desktop
- Upstash key names if you reset data often
- Personal runbook only you need

Public README stays minimal; details live in your local `DEPLOYMENT.private.md` only.